Telethon
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a 24-hour TV charity fund-raising event; a television programme to raise money for charity, where viewers telephone the comperes to pledge donations over many hours or days
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
